<div>
  <h2> Specimens batch load </h2>

  <div class="flexbox full_viewport_whitespace">
    <div class="item item1 one_third_width">
      <h3> Description and requirements </h3>

      <p> Creates collection objects from a Castor to TaxonWorks exported collection objects file. Attaches at most 4 identifiers of type Identifier::Local::CollectionObject to each collection object.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>A tab-delimited, UTF-8 compatible text file is required.</li>
        <li>Column headers are here <%= link_to('sample template', asset_path('batch_load_templates/collection_objects/collection_objects_specimens_batch_load.tab'), target: '_blank') -%>).</li>
        <li>Multiple uploads of the same data will do something, not sure.</li>
        <li>Only creates collection objects if the column value of "locality_code_prefix" of the current row is "DRM"</li>
        <li>There is currently some|no size limit to the file being loaded but this may change in the future.</li>
        <li>Assumes a namespace with name "Castor" and shortname "CTR" exists</li>
        <li>Assumes a namespace with name "Morphbank" and shortname "MBK" exists</li>
        <li>Assumes a namespace with name "DRMLabVoucher" and shortname "DRMLV" exists</li>
        <li>Assumes a namespace with name "DRMFieldVoucher" and shortname "DRMFV" exists</li>
        <li>Assumes a namespace with name "DRMFieldNumbers" and shortname "DRMFN" exists</li>
        <li>Identifier with namespace Castor will be attached with the value of the "guid" column if not blank</li>
        <li>Identifier with namespace Morphbank will be attached with the value of the "morphbank_specimen_id" column if not blank</li>
        <li>Identifier with namespace DRMLabVoucher will be attached with the value of the "specimen_number" column if not blank</li>
        <li>Identifier with namespace DRMFieldVoucher will be attached with the value of the "voucher_number_prefix" + "voucher_number_stirng" column if not blank</li>
        <li>Only links to a collecting event that has an attached Identifier with namespace Castor and with a value that matches this objects "collecting_event_guid" column</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="item item2 one_third_width">
      <h3> Example file </h3>

      <p> Part of the example tab delimited formatted file. 
        In the example whitespace is a tab. View sample file template.</p>

      <pre class="fixed_width_font">guid morphbank_specimen_id sample_code_prefix sample_code suffix det_confidence id_notes locality_code_prefix locality_code_string...</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="item item3">
      <h3> Go! </h3>
      <%= render partial: '/collection_objects/batch_load/specimens/form', locals: {url: preview_specimens_batch_load_collection_objects_path, submit: :preview} -%>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
